KnownSpaces.Name: Char3_CollisionLayer
KnownSpaces.Comment:
This variable... is so weird!

Everything non-infintely-high wall is a floor.
Any floor above this value is treated as a wall/ceiling.

Also ceilings are actually floors on different layers.
